-- Microsoft Sells 302,000 Xbox Consoles in February
-- B y   C l i f f   E d w a r d s
-- 2013-03-14T22:19:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-14/microsoft-sells-302-000-xbox-consoles-in-february.html
Microsoft Corp. (MSFT)  said U.S. retailers
sold 302,000 Xbox 360 games consoles in February, citing data by
NPD Group Inc.  It was the 26th consecutive month Redmond, Washington-based
Microsoft led console sales, it said in a statement. Its
machines account for 41 percent of current-generation console
sales. Microsoft sold 426,000 Xbox 360 units a year ago.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cliff Edwards in San Francisco at 
